{"tid":2167793,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"長江口今晨砂石油輪兩船相撞 江面如火海","createTime":"2020-08-21T10:32:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T11:51:09.000Z","uid":103294,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"b78ca0c02a40fc40be23ece08a1d102477c58aa7","tid":2167793,"uid":103294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T10:32:33.000Z","msg":"中國上海長江口20日凌晨發生兩艘船隻碰撞的嚴重事故，一艘運油船與砂石貨船發生碰撞，造成油船起火，砂石料船沉沒，以及14人失蹤，目前搜救行動仍持續進行。消息一出，許多網友紛紛留言希望能儘快找到失蹤的船員，也有不少網友質疑，事故原因恐與內河船到海上偷運砂石有關。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1vDwDEY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1vDwDEY.jpg&h=d43770c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據東森新聞報道說，運油船、砂石船相撞，上海長江口外海陷火海，17人僅3人獲救。該消息說，長江口外海運油船與砂石貨船兩船相撞，使海面陷入一片火海。<br />\n<br />\n根據中國上海海事局官方微博報導，事發時間為20日凌晨3點39分，當時一艘載運約3000噸汽油的油船與一艘運砂船在長江口燈船東南約1.5海里處發生碰撞，隨後運油船甲板起火燃燒，運砂船沉沒，油船14人，砂石料船3人，兩船共17人僅3人獲救，其中1人須送醫治療。事故發生後，上海各部門也緊急調派直升機與船艇前往搶救，同時也發布航行警告，公布沉船位置並畫定現場警戒區域，以確保周邊船舶航行安全和航道暢通。<br />\n<br />\n報道引據新京報消息，下午3時許，搜救工作仍在進行，東海救102搜救船返回碼頭補給泡沫，泡沫主要用於撲滅水上的流淌火以及船上的油起火。經過一上午的救援，現場火情已得到進一步控制。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20200820-%E9%95%B7%E6%B1%9F%E5%8F%A3%E4%BB%8A%E6%99%A8%E7%A0%82%E7%9F%B3%E6%B2%B9%E8%BC%AA%E5%85%A9%E8%88%B9%E7%9B%B8%E6%92%9E-%E6%B1%9F%E9%9D%A2%E5%A6%82%E7%81%AB%E6%B5%B7?ref=fb_i\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20200820-%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%25B1%259F%25E5%258F%25A3%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%2599%25A8%25E7%25A0%2582%25E7%259F%25B3%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E8%25BC%25AA%25E5%2585%25A9%25E8%2588%25B9%25E7%259B%25B8%25E6%2592%259E-%25E6%25B1%259F%25E9%259D%25A2%25E5%25A6%2582%25E7%2581%25AB%25E6%25B5%25B7%3Fref%3Dfb_i&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu8v4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=2fd92e29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20200820-%E9%95%B7%E6%B1%9F%E5%8F%A3%E4%BB%8A%E6%99%A8%E7%A0%82%E7%9F%B3%E6%B2%B9%E8%BC%AA%E5%85%A9%E8%88%B9%E7%9B%B8%E6%92%9E-%E6%B1%9F%E9%9D%A2%E5%A6%82%E7%81%AB%E6%B5%B7?ref=fb_i</a>"},{"pid":"d570a46ccbe8a96580999ef2b18a5f531ae248af","tid":2167793,"uid":32511,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T10:34:36.000Z","msg":"火燒赤迫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0ec67a9edf3629b5829cf28d7aa173bb0be301","tid":2167793,"uid":171313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T10:35:08.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"7795a92cc03778fb8d79dae30a1d85d1d41700bb","tid":2167793,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T10:37:28.000Z","msg":"雄火烈焰先夠氣勢<br />\n美國廢青做唔做到先？"},{"pid":"621a528fb0a4e5cad5a76f4592f5e68aae1d6054","tid":2167793,"uid":126508,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T10:42:14.000Z","msg":"一定唔關北斗事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f01a9bfe8b3b13b8a80310d41d07815197df50e9","tid":2167793,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T10:49:00.000Z","msg":"矛盾對決<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 油 vs 沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a55b219cf911855396cf72d487de3cdad129c2af","tid":2167793,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T10:50:35.000Z","msg":"係咪軍演"},{"pid":"46aca879bee76559e11a1754d8ac3cbda9b2703b","tid":2167793,"uid":230594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T10:53:51.000Z","msg":"拍電影啫 無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"823e1ef7d945860f50aa66b2d2e74c56d9c26238","tid":2167793,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T10:54:40.000Z","msg":"多難興邦.jpg"},{"pid":"8a5579cb50b0238665078a1d1320c42f393054b0","tid":2167793,"uid":103294,"like":3,"dislike